sentences: Mike Piersante won two Grammy Awards in 2009 for his work as Engineer/Mixer.
Krauss and Plant sang this track as a duet which was released on the album Raising Sand, available on Rounder which won another 2009 Grammy for Mike Piersante for Album of the Year.
